    "name": {
      "zh": "Oakley Mechanism重型背包 Black",
      "en": "Oakley Mechanism heavy duty backpack (Black)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Mechanism",
      "en": "Mechanism"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 109,118₽ | 物品价值: 55,238 | Ragman报价: 34,248₽容器效率: x1.28 (32/25)\n\n购买渠道 @ Ragman 等级2 < 67,446₽\n购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 71,809₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级2 < GP x17 | Σ ≈ 127,500₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级2 < 剪线钳 x2 | Σ ≈ 36,766₽\n\nMechanism背包提供可以适应任何冒险的多功能耐用结构。重型金属夹子、拉链和钩环闭合装置可提供安全的存储空间，而顶部翻盖开口则意味着更大的空间可用于搬运更大的物品。各种专用口袋提供军式设计的配置让您能方便的使用。加垫可调式肩带，让您每次外出都能保持舒适。 ",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 109,118₽ | 物品价值: 55,238 | Ragman报价: 34,248₽容器效率: x1.28 (32/25)\n\n购买渠道 @ Ragman 等级2 < 67,446₽\n购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 71,809₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级2 < GP x17 | Σ ≈ 127,500₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级2 < 剪线钳 x2 | Σ ≈ 36,766₽\n\nThe Mechanism backpack offers versatility and durable construction that accommodates any adventure. Heavy-duty metal clips, zips, and hook-and-loop closures create secure storage, and a flap-top opening means more room for hauling larger items. A variety of specialized pockets deliver military-style organization and easy access, and padded adjustable shoulder straps keep every excursion comfortable."
    },
